BT 0 g /F2 20 Tf 200.4 720 Td (Chapter 1: Lights Out!) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 710 m 540 710 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (It was a normal Tuesday evening when suddenly - everything went dark.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 664 Td (The lights, the TV, the computer, the refrigerator - all silent. A blackout!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 648 Td (Zara sat in the darkness, amazed at how quiet everything was without electricity.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 632 Td ('We depend on electricity for EVERYTHING!' she realized, lighting a candle.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 616 Td (No phone charging, no microwave, no hot water, no internet!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 600 Td ('I never thought about where electricity comes from,' Zara whispered. 'Until now.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 72 564 Td (THE SCIENCE: WHAT IS ELECTRICITY?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 544 Td (Electricity is the flow of tiny particles called electrons through a material.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (Electrons are incredibly tiny - part of every atom in the universe.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 512 Td (When electrons flow in the same direction, we call it electric current.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 496 Td (Electric current is measured in amperes \(amps\) - like measuring water flow.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 480 Td (Voltage is the 'push' that makes electrons flow \(like water pressure in a pipe\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 464 Td (Electricity moves at nearly the speed of light - 186,000 miles per second!) Tj ET
q 0.92 g 67 374 478 89 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 77 433 Td (SCIENCE FACT BOX) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 413 Td (* The average home uses about 30 kilowatt-hours of electricity per day.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 395 Td (* Electricity was not 'invented' - it is a natural force. We learned to harness it!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 377 Td (* Electric eels can produce up to 860 volts - enough to stun a horse!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 344 Td (TRY THIS!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 328 Td (List everything in your home that uses electricity. How many items can you count?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 308 Td (THINK ABOUT IT:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 10 Tf 82 292 Td (What would life be like if electricity had never been harnessed?) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
