BT 0 g /F2 20 Tf 166.8 720 Td (Chapter 5: Magnets and Motors) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 710 m 540 710 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (Zara discovered something amazing: electricity and magnetism are connected!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 664 Td ('When electricity flows through a wire, it creates a magnetic field around it!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 648 Td (She wrapped wire around a nail and connected it to a battery. The nail became a magnet!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 632 Td ('An electromagnet! I can turn it on and off!' Zara was thrilled.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 616 Td ('This is how electric motors work - electromagnets spinning inside them!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 600 Td ('Motors are in everything: fans, washing machines, electric cars, even phones!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 72 564 Td (THE SCIENCE: ELECTROMAGNETISM) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 544 Td (Moving electricity creates magnetism; moving magnets create electricity!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (An electromagnet is made by wrapping wire around iron and running current through it.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 512 Td (Electric motors use electromagnets to convert electrical energy into spinning motion.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 496 Td (Generators do the opposite: spinning magnets near wire creates electricity!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 480 Td (This connection was discovered by Michael Faraday in 1831 - it powers our world!) Tj ET
q 0.92 g 67 390 478 89 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 77 449 Td (SCIENCE FACT BOX) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 429 Td (* MRI machines in hospitals use super-powerful electromagnets to see inside your body.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 411 Td (* Junkyard cranes use electromagnets to pick up cars - turn off the magnet, car drops!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 393 Td (* Earth itself is a giant magnet \(that is how compasses work!\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 360 Td (TRY THIS!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 344 Td (Wrap insulated wire around a nail 50 times, connect to a battery. Pick up paper clips - electromagnet!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 324 Td (THINK ABOUT IT:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 10 Tf 82 308 Td (Why is an electromagnet more useful than a regular magnet?) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
