BT 0 g /F2 20 Tf 181.2 720 Td (Chapter 6: The Power Plant) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 710 m 540 710 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td ('So where does all the electricity in our homes actually COME from?' Zara wondered.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 664 Td (She researched power plants - huge facilities that generate electricity for cities.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 648 Td ('Most power plants spin giant generators using steam, water, or wind!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 632 Td ('The spinning magnets inside generators push electrons through miles of wires.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 616 Td ('Then electricity travels through power lines all the way to our homes!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 600 Td (Zara was amazed that the same basic principle \(spinning magnets\) powers everything.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 72 564 Td (THE SCIENCE: GENERATING ELECTRICITY) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 544 Td (Coal/Gas plants: Burn fuel to boil water, steam spins turbines, turbines spin generators.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (Hydroelectric: Falling water spins turbines \(like at dams and waterfalls\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 512 Td (Wind power: Wind spins turbine blades connected to generators.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 496 Td (Solar power: Sunlight hits special cells that directly convert light to electricity!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 480 Td (Nuclear: Splitting atoms creates heat, boils water, steam spins turbines.) Tj ET
q 0.92 g 67 390 478 89 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 77 449 Td (SCIENCE FACT BOX) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 429 Td (* Power travels through lines at nearly light speed - coast to coast in milliseconds!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 411 Td (* Solar panels have no moving parts - photons knock electrons loose in silicon cells.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 393 Td (* One wind turbine can power about 1,500 homes!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 360 Td (TRY THIS!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 344 Td (Spin a magnet near a coil of wire connected to an LED. Can you make it flicker? That is a generator!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 324 Td (THINK ABOUT IT:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 10 Tf 82 308 Td (What are the advantages and disadvantages of solar vs coal power?) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
