BT 0 g /F2 20 Tf 190.8 720 Td (Chapter 7: Saving Energy) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 710 m 540 710 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (After learning where electricity comes from, Zara realized something important.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 664 Td ('Burning coal and gas to make electricity creates pollution and CO2!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 648 Td ('If we use less electricity, power plants burn less fuel and pollute less!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 632 Td (She made a plan: turn off lights when leaving rooms, unplug chargers, use less AC.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 616 Td ('Renewable sources like solar and wind do not pollute at all!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 600 Td ('The future of energy is clean, renewable, and exciting!' Zara declared.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 72 564 Td (THE SCIENCE: ENERGY CONSERVATION) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 544 Td (Renewable energy: sun, wind, water, geothermal - they never run out!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (Non-renewable energy: coal, oil, natural gas - limited supply, creates pollution.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 512 Td (LED bulbs use 75% less energy than old incandescent bulbs for the same light!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 496 Td (Energy efficiency means getting the same result while using less electricity.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 480 Td (Even turning off a game console \(not standby\) saves electricity over a year!) Tj ET
q 0.92 g 67 390 478 89 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 77 449 Td (SCIENCE FACT BOX) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 429 Td (* If everyone in the US turned off one light for one hour, it would save enough energy for 1M homes!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 411 Td (* The Sun provides more energy to Earth in one hour than humans use in an entire year.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 393 Td (* Electric cars are 3-4 times more efficient than gasoline cars.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 360 Td (TRY THIS!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 344 Td (Do an energy audit: walk through your home and list everything using electricity. What could you turn off?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 324 Td (THINK ABOUT IT:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 10 Tf 82 308 Td (How could your school use less electricity without losing comfort?) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
