BT 0 g /F2 20 Tf 205.2 720 Td (Chapter 8: Lights On!) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 710 m 540 710 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (After 24 hours, the power finally came back on. CLICK! The lights returned!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 664 Td (But Zara looked at everything differently now. She understood the magic behind it all.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 648 Td ('Every light switch, every phone charge, every song from a speaker...') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 632 Td ('...it is all electrons flowing through circuits, powered by spinning generators!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 616 Td (She turned off the lights she did not need and smiled.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 600 Td ('Knowledge really IS power - literally!' Zara laughed at her own joke.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 72 564 Td (MORAL:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F5 12 Tf 72 546 Td (Knowledge is power - literally! Understanding electricity helps us) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F5 12 Tf 72 530 Td (use it wisely and build a cleaner, brighter future for everyone.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 500 Td (What Zara learned on her journey:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 484 Td (  - Electricity is the flow of electrons through conductors) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 468 Td (  - Circuits need a complete path for electricity to flow) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 452 Td (  - Batteries convert chemical energy to electrical energy) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 436 Td (  - Electromagnetism connects electricity and magnetism) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 420 Td (  - Generators spin magnets to create electricity) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 404 Td (  - Renewable energy is the future - solar, wind, and water power!) Tj ET
q 0.92 g 67 314 478 89 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 77 373 Td (SCIENCE FACT BOX) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 353 Td (* Nikola Tesla and Thomas Edison competed to bring electricity to homes in the 1880s.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 335 Td (* Today, about 1 billion people worldwide still lack access to electricity.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 317 Td (* YOU could be the scientist who invents the next big energy breakthrough!) Tj ET

